{
  "id": "adv_main_01_06_04",
  "title": "星見編2章19話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（数日後）\n（今日は東京でダンスレッスンを受ける日だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（—A few days later）\n（Today‚ the girls are having dance lessons in Tokyo.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 5.933333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 6.033333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "伊吹さん。前にも言ったけど、もっと自信を持って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ as I told you last time‚ you need to have more self-confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "思い切って、自分を表現して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Express yourself! Don’t hold back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.733333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "気持ちで負けたらダメよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t let your feelings trip you up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあ今のところ、もう一回！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ let’s repeat that last part. Again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.934009742736794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん\n渚ちゃん……大丈夫かな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}.\nDo you think Nagisa is okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.07228247324624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "実はいい偶然があってさ\nもしかしたら、うまくいくかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ due to a lucky coincidence‚\nthings just might go her way today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.27228247324624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "いい偶然って？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What lucky coincidence?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.77228247324624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうどそろそろだな\nみんな、ちょっと聞いてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s going to happen soon.\nHey‚ girls‚ listen up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.275933225949586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "実はだな、今日は隣の部屋でTRINITYAiLEも\nレッスンをしているそうなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You see‚ I heard that today‚ in the next room over‚\nTRINITYAiLE also has their lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEが……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE is here?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリを狙うライバルではあるが\nそれ以前に芸能界の先輩でもある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While they are your rivals in the Grand Prix‚\nthey’re also your senpai idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースは挨拶済みだけど\nみんなはまだだったろ？　こっちに来てくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace has already paid their respects‚\nbut the rest of you haven’t yet. Come with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "え、今？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな、急ですわよ……！\n待ちなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but this is all so sudden!\nWait a minute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2300.000000000004,
          "startTime": 62.56666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 63
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-com001.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、星見プロダクション所属\n『月のテンペスト』の長瀬琴乃です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-representing Hoshimi Productions‚\nI’m Moon Tempest’s Kotono Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "い、伊吹渚です\nよろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m Nagisa Ibuki.\nmore trouble in the future!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-com005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣だよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m Mei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-com004.m4a",
      "text": "成宮すずですわ\n成宮と聞いてピンときた人もいるかもしれないけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am Suzu Narumiya.\nThe name Narumiya probably rings a bell. That is because—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-com003.m4a",
      "text": "すずさん、今は自重してください\n……白石沙季です。よろしくお願いいたします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ please show some restraint.\nI’m Saki Shiraishi. A pleasure to make your acquaintance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーの{user}です\n本日はお時間をいただきありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m {user}‚ their manager.\nThank you very much for giving us some of your time today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそ、わざわざご挨拶ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Likewise‚ thanks for coming to say hi to all of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEの天動瑠依です\nみなさん、よろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m Rui Tendo of TRINITYAiLE.\nNice to meet you‚ ladies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "奥山すみれです！\n一緒にグランプリ、がんばりましょうね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire Okuyama here!\nGood luck at the Grand Prix! Let’s all do our best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "うちは鈴村優いいます\nよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The name’s Yu Suzumura.\nPlease‚ set it up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、いえっ\nよ、よろしくお願いしますっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! It’s nothing.\nN-nice to meet you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "五人もいると賑やかで楽しそうね\n優、私達もメンバー増やそうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The group sure is lively when there are five people.\nYu‚ think we should add some members?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ほんならうちは、さっきからこっち見てる\nそこの可愛い子がええなあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe! If I get to choose‚ I’d like that cute girl\nwho won’t stop staring at me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_04-com002.m4a",
      "text": "え、えええ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Huh？？？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
